<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profile Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .profile-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .profile-photo {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .profile-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .profile-surname {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .profile-info {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="profile-container">
        <!-- Use a relative or correctly formatted path for the image -->
        <img src=""images/img.av.png"" alt="Profile Photo" class="profile-photo">
        
        <h1 class="profile-name">Devon</h1>
        <h2 class="profile-surname">Swift</h2>
        <p class="profile-info">
            <strong>About:</strong><br>
            Devon Swift is an experienced full-stack web developer with a passion for creating intuitive, dynamic, and user-friendly websites and applications. With over 5 years in the industry, Devon has developed expertise in a variety of technologies, including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Python. He is proficient in both front-end and back-end development, with strong knowledge in frameworks like React, Node.js, and Django.
        </p>
        <a href="/person/hobby">Hobby</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
